      "TrialObjectives": "To study the side effects and best dose of yttrium Y 90 glass microspheres when given together with capecitabine in treating patients with liver cholangiocarcinoma or liver metastases.  To establish the maximally tolerated dose of yttrium Y 90 glass microspheres in combination with capecitabine in patients with intrahepatic cholangiocarcinoma or liver metastases.  To characterize the toxicity of this regimen in these patients.  To determine the time to tumor progression in these patients.",
      "ObjectivePrimaryEndPoint": "Primary Outcome Measures: Maximal tolerated dose of yttrium Y 90 [ Time Frame: During treatment and any time up to 6 weeks post-treatment ] Toxicity [ Time Frame: During treatment and up to 30 days post-treatment ] Time to tumor progression [ Time Frame: At time of disease progression ]  Primary Endpoint: To determine the maximum tolerated dose of Y90 with capecitabine.",
