      "TreatmentPlan": "Arms CC-115: Experimental  Drug: CC-115 Part A (actively recruiting): Dose level starts with 0.5 mg daily by mouth in cycles of 28 days. Level increases for different patient cohorts in 100% or 50% increments until optimal dose schedule is established for further study. Treatment continues for as long as patient benefits ((i.e., until disease progression or unacceptable toxicity). Part B: Optimal dose schedule is administered in 28-day cycles until disease progression. ASCO 2016: CC-115 given orally once or twice daily until disease progression in dose escalation and expansion cohorts.",
